headline: LYV Q2 Deep Dive: International Expansion and Venue Strategy Drive Growth
summary: Live events and entertainment company Live Nation (NYSE:LYV) announced better-than-expected revenue in Q2 CY2025, with sales up 16.3% year on year to $7.01 billion. Its non-GAAP profit of $1.04 per share was 1.5% above analysts’ consensus estimates.
